name: south-sudan-operational-presence
notes: The Who does What Where is a core humanitarian dataset for coordination. This data contains operational presence of humanitarian partners in South Sudan at Admin 2 level.

organization.name: ocha-south-sudan
organization.title: OCHA South Sudan
organization.description: OCHA is the part of the United Nations Secretariat responsible for bringing together humanitarian actors to ensure a coherent response to emergencies. OCHA also ensures there is a framework within which each actor can contribute to the overall response effort.
